      "writtenOn": "2022-04-28T06:31:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Hmm, this also hit a corner in gerrit where two CLs in the same project have the same Change-ID: this change and aosp/2078920.  If I hadn\u0027t abandoned this change, I could have updated the change to do a `repo upload` and check which CL gerrit picks to update or if it just blows up.",
      "parentUuid": "2ee872e5_cf523173",
      "revId": "24ad50770788d312b697609722a23a393070f67b",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889"
    },
    {
