        "id": 1010056
      },
      "writtenOn": "2022-04-28T06:36:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Maybe it is worth filing a bug report for the gerrit folks that even this case happened. I don\u0027t know how their \"eventual consistency\" really is intended to work, but I don\u0027t think having 2 CLs with the same Change-ID is expected by the Android developers.",
      "parentUuid": "51b07625_a5f76b21",
      "revId": "24ad50770788d312b697609722a23a393070f67b",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889"
